results.name: Decimal expansion of the real Stieltjes gamma function at x = 3/2, negated.
comment: See A301816 for comments and references.
formula: c = Re((4/5)*Pi*Integral_{-oo..oo} log(1/2+i*z)^(5/2)/(exp(-Pi*z)+exp(Pi*z))^2 dz) where i is the imaginary unit.
maple: Sti := x -> (4*Pi/(x + 1))*int(log(1/2 + I*z)^(x + 1)/(exp(-Pi*z) + exp(Pi*z))^2, z=0..64): Sti(3/2): Re(evalf(%,100)); # Note that this is an approximation which needs a larger domain of integration and higher precision if used for more values than are in the Data section.
results.author: _Peter Luschny_, Apr 09 2018
